name: Cargolux 747-8R7F Landing in Calgary
description:
HAPPY HEAVY AIRCRAFT FRIDAY!
Hey everyone, this is a Cargolux Airlines International Boeing 747-8R7F landing at Calgary International Airport. This is my first time seeing one of these monsters, and this particular aircraft was only with Cargolux for 3 weeks when this was shot! I hope you enjoy, and please comment, rate, and subscribe!

FLIGHT INFO
